    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Fringe e-ticket Tent</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/223645748/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Fringe e-ticket Tent" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/68/223645748_8ddb0b44ab_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>A vast improvement over the mile-long queue at the High Street box office -- You just surf the Fringe website on one of forty PCs, order online, then pick your tickets up at the desk.</p>
        </p>

