<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Joy, Asleep, Kilmainham Gaol, Dublin.</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/219047416/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Joy, Asleep, Kilmainham Gaol, Dublin." src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/96/219047416_063b2ac559_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Joy hadn't had enough sleep, and her epilepsy was playing up, so for her, the walking tour of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kilmainham_Gaol">Kilmainham Gaol</a> was more of a napping-and-leaning tour.</p>
        </p>

